{
  "texts": [
    "Moreover, they gain access to higher-order thinking skills, integrative learning experiences, and opportunities for personal and social growth.The study underscores the significance of AI research in higher education, highlighting key developments.",
    "However, research on learning management systems, mobile learning systems, parallel robots, training, interactive test dashboards, and virtual assistants remains limited in Nigeria.",
    "Recommendations are proposed for structuring AI research and establishing supportive policies based on uncovered findings, advocating for the integration of cutting-edge practices from advanced nations into Nigerian educational institutions.",
    "These practices, though underutilized, have the potential to promote AI utilization in higher education, enrich student learning experiences, and enhance student engagement.",
    "Specifically, the emphasis should be on implementing educational software employing AI techniques such as data mining and machine learning approaches, mirroring successful strategies adopted elsewhere.Contribution to Knowledge: This work significantly contributes to existing knowledge by aiding academics and educators in understanding the current status and progress of AI applications in Nigerian higher education."
  ]
}